@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
actor User
participant "Browser" as Browser
participant "App.jsx" as App
participant "api/client.js" as Client
participant "FastAPI" as API

== Initial load ==
User -> Browser : Open application
Browser -> App : mount()
App -> Client : loadWorkspaceData()

par fetch health
  Client -> API : GET /health
  API --> Client : health payload
else fetch overview
  Client -> API : GET /api/overview
  API --> Client : overview payload
else fetch campaigns workspace
  Client -> API : GET /api/campaigns/workspace
  API --> Client : campaigns payload
else fetch job automation workspace
  Client -> API : GET /api/job-automation/workspace
  API --> Client : job automation payload
else fetch day report
  Client -> API : GET /api/day-report/dashboard
  API --> Client : day report payload
else fetch submissions
  Client -> API : GET /api/submissions/dashboard
  API --> Client : submissions payload
end

Client --> App : aggregated workspace data
App --> Browser : render routes and pages

== API Explorer flow ==
User -> Browser : Open /api-explorer
Browser -> Client : fetchApiEndpointCatalog()
Client -> API : GET /api/meta/endpoints
API --> Client : endpoint catalog
Client --> Browser : render endpoint request/response examples
@enduml
